<p><strong>项目等级：</strong>Safe</p>
<p><strong>特殊收容措施：</strong>SCP-CN-1686-AP-1被收容在特定收容所中，确保SCP-CN-1686-AP-1个体不会受到进一步的损害。</p>



<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2013/06/07/21/51/torture-chair-122858_960_720.jpg" style="width:300px;" class="enlarge" alt="torture-chair-122858_960_720.jpg" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
